import csv
from operator import itemgetter 
import jieba
import pandas as pd
jieba.set_dictionary('dict.txt.big.txt')  #不一定要設定詞庫，內建的效果也不錯

freq_dict = {}

with open('all_flix_caption.csv', 'r') as f:
    flix_df = pd.read_csv(f)
    print(flix_df.columns)
    EVENT, MESSAGE_ID, TITLE, VALUE= flix_df.columns
    for title in flix_df[TITLE]:
        for token in jieba.cut(title, cut_all=False, HMM=True):
            if token in freq_dict.keys():
                freq_dict[token]+=1
            else:
                freq_dict[token]=1
print(freq_dict)                
res = dict(sorted(freq_dict.items(), key = itemgetter(1), reverse = True)[:400]) 

with open('TOP 400 keywords.csv', 'w') as f:
    for key in res.keys():
        f.write("%s,%s\n"%(key,res[key]))

# 文字雲
%matplotlib inline
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from wordcloud import WordCloud
from PIL import Image
import jieba
import numpy as np
import re

text = ""
# 如果檔案內有一些編碼錯誤，使用 errors='ignore' 來忽略錯誤
with open('all_flix_caption.csv', 'r') as f:
    flix_df = pd.read_csv(f)
    EVENT, MESSAGE_ID, TITLE, VALUE= flix_df.columns
    for title in flix_df[TITLE]:
        title = re.sub('[a-zA-Z0-9’!"#$%&\'()*+,-./:;<=>?@，。?★、…【】《》？“”‘’！[\\]^_`{|}~\s]+', "", title)
#         title = re.sub('[\001\002\003\004\005\006\007\x08\x09\x0a\x0b\x0c\x0d\x0e\x0f\x10\x11\x12\x13\x14\x15\x16\x17\x18\x19\x1a]+', '', title)
        text += title
# 設定使用 big5 斷詞
jieba.set_dictionary('dict.txt.big.txt')
wordlist = jieba.cut(text)
words = " ".join(wordlist)
#文字雲造型圖片
# mask = np.array(Image.open('picture.png')) #文字雲形狀
# 從 Google 下載的中文字型
font = 'SourceHanSansTW-Regular.otf'
#背景顏色預設黑色，改為白色、使用指定圖形、使用指定字體
# my_wordcloud = WordCloud(background_color='white',mask=mask,font_path=font).generate(words)
my_wordcloud = WordCloud(background_color='white', width=1600, height=900,font_path=font).generate(words)

plt.figure(figsize = (16,9))
plt.imshow(my_wordcloud)
plt.axis("off")
plt.show()
#存檔
my_wordcloud.to_file('word_cloud.png')
